---
title: Cheesy Fiesta Black Bean Burger with Fries & Smokey Aioli
description: Here we go, it’s another combo that’s going make mouths water and stomachs rumble. Our two stars tonight are black bean fritters and a burger, transforming into a fritter burger that deserves a standing ovation!

